      ),
      'value' => '<p>Special events that fall outside of the realm of presentations, panels, keynotes and so on can also be added to the conference schedule. Clicking on the Special Events link available from the Scheduler page will bring the Conference Manager to the Special Events page, where events can be created, added and deleted. To create a new event the Conference Manager must click on the Create a New Special Event link, fill out the name of the event; the date; the start and end time; and add a description, if needed. Since it is not possible to assign these events to buildings and rooms, it is advisable to put location information and directions in the description.</p>',
